{"tid":2264043,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麻撚煩系列-泰式豬頸肉沙律","createTime":"2020-10-30T10:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T11:41:06.000Z","uid":68594,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47e7d6ef3a131c09221fae908145b081315f5a5e","tid":2264043,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"大家好！我係子言張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說我諗都有差唔多成年冇飛過，相信大家都好掛住去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過始終武漢肺炎嚴重！我哋都<br />\n<br />\n係保持社交距離，今日就唯有整一個泰式沙律望梅止渴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然需要材料比較多，但係製作簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個沙律惹味又開胃，自己整多多都食得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GHXSBlNJmws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGHXSBlNJmws&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=4366e1f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GHXSBlNJmws</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴材料<br />\n豬頸肉..........2塊<br />\n青瓜.........1條<br />\n甘筍..........半條<br />\n紫洋蔥........半個<br />\n蒜頭..........4-5瓣<br />\n蔥...............1紥<br />\n香茅..........少許<br />\n青檸.........兩粒<br />\n辣椒..........3-4隻<br />\n車厘茄...........8-10粒<br />\n芫茜..........1紥<br />\n金不換........1紥<br />\n(炸乾蔥..........少許)<br />\n(炸蒜頭碎...........少許)<br />\n<br />\n🔴調味料<br />\n紹興酒、生抽、魚露、胡椒粉、鹽、糖、雞粉、生粉、(泰式辣醬)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔴步驟(預備部分)：<br />\n1.豬頸肉對半切開<br />\n2.倒入兩至三圈魚露、半蓋紹興酒、兩至三圈生抽、兩匙糖、兩匙生粉<br />\n3.少許芫茜、少許蔥、一隻辣椒切碎再加到碗內<br />\n4.撈勻後用保鮮紙包好放入雪櫃冷藏30分鐘或以上<br />\n5.紫洋蔥切成幼絲、甘筍切絲、青瓜刨成青瓜絲、車厘茄對半切開<br />\n6.香茅用少許莖部的部分切碎、摘出金不換的葉、蔥切成蔥花、芫茜切碎、三隻辣椒切碎、青檸後對半切開、蒜頭切碎<br />\n<br />\n🔴步驟(調配醬汁)：<br />\n1.倒入三至四湯匙生抽、三至四湯匙魚露、四匙糖<br />\n2.唧入青檸汁，隔走青檸籽<br />\n3.倒入蒜頭碎、辣椒碎、芫茜、蔥花、香茅碎<br />\n4.用筷子撈勻，如果覺得唔夠汁，可多加點魚露<br />\n<br />\n🔴步驟(煎豬頸肉)：<br />\n1.冷鑊落油，油熱後用大火煎豬頸肉，兩至三分鐘後翻轉<br />\n2.倒入半杯熱水，轉成細火並冚蓋，煮10-15分鐘<br />\n3.途中煮至沒有水，記得倒多半杯水，直至把豬頸肉煮腍<br />\n4.夾起豬頸肉並等待待豬頸肉冷卻<br />\n<br />\n🔴步驟(組合部分)：<br />\n1.豬頸肉切成條狀<br />\n2.隨個人喜好於醬汁內倒入了泰式辣醬<br />\n3.把青瓜、車厘茄、紫洋蔥、甘筍放到大碗內<br />\n4.豬頸肉鋪上配料上、倒入醬汁<br />\n5.鋪上金不換、芫茜、蔥花、炸乾蔥及炸蒜頭碎<br />\n6.吃之前把所有食材及醬汁撈勻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意我呢段片嘅朋友可以俾個like我啦或者可以訂閱我嘅Channel嘅！我哋下一段片再見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n►Youtube：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/子言張\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2F%E5%AD%90%E8%A8%80%E5%BC%B5&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=c9c9ce3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/子言張</a>"},{"pid":"4393db77ad3b99b55a736be3aa3a43ecf1fa1f38","tid":2264043,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb084dedb0897537a99ad9f61078ed157c997e80","tid":2264043,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db4542585ff699b91d3157a21eabf5b2cca085a","tid":2264043,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb084dedb0897537a99ad9f61078ed157c997e80","tid":2264043,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然真係好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過真係好好食"},{"pid":"6fef7fa417dcdb7d4250b074c94805c60006b67a","tid":2264043,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}